I wish it right now. God?

01:34:01.910 --> 01:34:06.790
Hey? God?
You listening?

01:34:08.540 --> 01:34:11.880
You can't take her away.
Okay?

01:34:13.460 --> 01:34:15.880
I want her to stay here.

01:34:17.380 --> 01:34:22.010
It's not gonna work. You need
an anal probe and a morphine shooter.

01:34:30.560 --> 01:34:34.110
-Are you scared?
-No.

01:34:37.440 --> 01:34:39.040
Not anymore.

01:35:09.930 --> 01:35:11.530
Marley?

01:35:14.810 --> 01:35:16.240
Marley?

01:35:22.320 --> 01:35:23.950
Marley?

01:35:27.450 --> 01:35:28.950
Hey-

01:35:30.290 --> 01:35:32.710
Marley...

01:35:58.770 --> 01:36:00.280
Here you go, sir.

01:36:01.940 --> 01:36:03.490
This is Peter.

01:36:09.830 --> 01:36:11.580
Ahh!

01:37:13.810 --> 01:37:16.530
Hey you, it's me.

01:37:17.980 --> 01:37:22.480
Oh, I didn't think
this was going to be so difficult.

01:37:22.570 --> 01:37:26.200
I thank God you came into my life.
I do.

01:37:26.280 --> 01:37:28.870
Because you showed me
how to be the person

01:37:28.950 --> 01:37:32.450
I always imagined myself to be.

01:37:32.530 --> 01:37:34.630
That's not even
giving you enough credit,

01:37:34.700 --> 01:37:38.500
because until I met you
I had no idea who I could be.

01:37:39.960 --> 01:37:46.090
So-- take care and try
not to fall in love again. Ever.

01:37:46.170 --> 01:37:47.850
Ever again.

01:37:49.840 --> 01:37:51.470
That's kind of a joke.

01:37:53.100 --> 01:37:55.690
-I love you.
-I love you.

01:38:12.570 --> 01:38:17.630
Oh, oh, oh.
I know.

01:38:51.030 --> 01:38:54.500
(voice over Marley)
So, that's my story.

01:38:54.570 --> 01:38:57.920
I had some pretty amazing friends,
didn't I?

01:38:57.990 --> 01:39:02.370
And I include my parents in that group,
even though my whole life I blamed them

01:39:02.460 --> 01:39:04.930
for, well, everything.

01:39:05.000 --> 01:39:10.800
But the truth is: I was afraid.
I was afraid to trust and forgive.

01:39:10.880 --> 01:39:14.680
I was scared I wasn't enough.
But I was.

01:39:31.780 --> 01:39:34.530
(Julian): I just have to say: To Marley.

01:39:34.610 --> 01:39:36.370
(Everyone): To Marley!

01:40:14.820 --> 01:40:17.370
-Thank you, Marley.
-Thank you, Marley.

01:40:21.830 --> 01:40:23.250
Hi.

01:40:30.840 --> 01:40:32.260
Stanley.

01:40:44.680 --> 01:40:47.360
(voice over Marley)
What I wouldn't give

01:40:47.440 --> 01:40:52.660
to experience just one more time,
to feel that incredible sensation

01:40:54.360 --> 01:40:58.990
when he looked at me
and I felt-- alive.

